OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWeather forecasters abused 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover heatwave coverage     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Weather forecasters faced unprecedented
OL,6, levels of trolling during this month's 
OL,7, extreme heat in the UK, according to   
OL,8, leading figures in the industry.       
OL,10,FThe BBC's team received hundreds of    
OL,11,Fabusive tweets or emails questioning   
OL,12,Ftheir reports and telling them to "get 
OL,13,Fa grip", as temperatures hit 40.C.     
OL,15,FBBC meteorologist Matt Taylor said he  
OL,16,Fhad never experienced anything like it 
OL,17,Fin nearly 25 years working in weather. 
OL,19,FThe Royal Meteorological Society       
OL,20,Fcondemned the trolling.                
